{"tid":216166,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"[報告] 搶先到手 智雲Smooth Q 開箱","createTime":"2017-04-25T02:57:48.000Z","updateTime":"2017-04-25T06:04:08.000Z","uid":19725,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"df1f7b4c8981671ad8c50ccb55839d66c7083d1e","tid":216166,"uid":19725,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-25T02:57:48.000Z","msg":"首先要多謝巴打雅仲 佢讓我拎先 如果唔係趕唔切去英國前收到 <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/04/25/103722_f785e978cbbc27741b93bee5a2678082.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F04%2F25%2F103722_f785e978cbbc27741b93bee5a2678082.jpg&h=37c4bfe6&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n幾經辛苦 終於收到 <br />\n因為全中國 甚至全世界都想買呢支Smooth Q 試玩 <br />\n缺貨問題我估未來1-2 個月會解決<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/04/25/104433_45df079e04c9c24bf880234659802a80.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F04%2F25%2F104433_45df079e04c9c24bf880234659802a80.jpg&h=c39cb1fd&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n睇得出智雲係想攻佔呢個手持穩定器既市場<br />\n呢個保護套真係我見過最靚 <br />\n唔係好硬 有d彈性 可以容易收藏<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/r3h1cK7.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fr3h1cK7.jpg&h=caa9b436&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n其他就無咩特別 <br />\n好似得呢個說明書同差電線<br />\n<br />\n本尊出現<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/7wTi2eF.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F7wTi2eF.jpg&h=ddc6b43a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n我買既本身係黑色 <br />\n但係因為缺貨到極點 <br />\n粗粗地用住灰先啦 睇落又唔錯 <br />\n質感係膠 但望落都似金屬 反而黑色就好膠<br />\n<br />\n試用報告：<br />\n穩定拍片好呢樣唔洗講 <br />\n對比其他3軸 我自己覺得都唔輸蝕 <br />\n佢其實都抄足DJI 又有全景 又有time lapse <br />\n小弟就未有時間 同天氣試足晒 <br />\n但係室內玩都唔錯 尤其佢ZY play 呢個apps <br />\n都可以較到拍片既quality 同埋iso 果d<br />\n呢個價位絕對對得住佢既質素 <br />\n<br />\n缺點：<br />\n渣得耐都會有少少攰 轉手使用就無問題<br />\n手感係膠 但呢個價位 算係咁啦 <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n價錢：<br />\n我買係優惠價679 因爲個期做緊返現 <br />\n呢家全部正價799 但其實都好抵玩 <br />\n我係同一間叫「海牙科技創新」買<br />\n佢大陸包郵，我用埋淘寶直送 送到附近既郵局<br />\n都係13 蚊rmb 抵過集運 仲要唔知會唔會壓到<br />\n同買Peak Design 一樣 只要用我「Drstrange」<br />\n呢個Coupon Code 就可以平69rmb 用730 蚊買到<br />\n但記住要去淘寶搵返同一間店鋪<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  <br />\n希望巴打們都會鍾意啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d9174dee63a94d8ff4b714f35f23d7f7a04390ce","tid":216166,"uid":22465,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-25T06:00:28.000Z","msg":"賣廣告，不了"},{"pid":"29b354933eedc1e037f51faf2f4ef6e603ebe221","tid":216166,"uid":13633,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-25T06:04:08.000Z","msg":"有無片睇"}]}